      "id": "PopularPost76118",
      "post_content": "I like using [Seal of Fire](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Seal of Fire) in order to play him on turn three.  \n  \nAfter he's in play, play [Flame Rift](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Flame Rift). In a 4 player game, he gets +12/+12 instantly, and Flame Rift is generally good in a red deck anyways.",
